. Set 
\begin_inset Formula \[
{\bar{\mathbf{F}}}=\left[\begin{array}{c|cccc}
\mathbf{F}_{0}+\mathbf{F}_{1}x^{\delta} & 0 & 0 & \cdots & 0 \\
\hline \mathbf{F}_{1}+\mathbf{F}_{2}x^{\delta} & \mathbf{I}_m & 0 & & \\
\mathbf{F}_{2}+\mathbf{F}_{3}x^{\delta} & 0 & \mathbf{I}_m & & \\ 
\vdots & & & \ddots & \\
\mathbf{F}_{l-1}+\mathbf{F}_{l}x^{\delta} & & & & \mathbf{I}_m
